channel.title: what's 'junk' for
channel.description: Posts in the discussion thread "what's 'junk' for" - what do you get from kicking junk

item.title: Re: what's 'junk' for
item.content:encoded:
You'll have to do all 4 junks.
Team must comprise of the paper for junk 1, w/ bones 2 for junk 2, mr. sandman for junk 3 and both goodboy and palm face must be at your team for junk 4.
After you've finished kicking all for junks you can now start and finish the junk showdown if you pass the special mission you'll have Thread joining you.
